title: Electricity prices for households in Denmark 2010 - 2019 , semi-annually
summary: Overall Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has increased over the Year.
Euro cents per kilowatt-hour is roughly constant from 2016_S2 to 2017_S1, and finally slightly increasing from 2017_S1 to 2018_S1.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2017_S2 and 2018_S1.
Maximum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, about 31.26 was reported at Year 2018_S1
The lowest Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, of value 30.1 was reported at Year 2017_S2
